### MotorView（揺らし処理本体）

DOTweenベースの揺らし処理を追加。`isWallHanging`フラグで物理/DOTweenを分岐。

#### [MODIFY] [MotorView.cs](file:///c:/God_Game_Creator_Evolution_2025_Remake/Beat_Shout_😱_Mansion/Assets/Mains/Scripts/Views/MotorView.cs)

**1. フィールド追加**

```diff
+    /// <summary>壁掛けオブジェクトか（DOTween揺らし使用）</summary>
+    private bool _isWallHanging;
+    /// <summary>壁掛けオブジェクトか（DOTween揺らし使用）</summary>
+    public bool IsWallHanging { set => _isWallHanging = value; }
+    /// <summary>壁掛け揺らしのDOTween Sequence</summary>
+    private Sequence _wallHangingShakeSequence;
+    /// <summary>BlendShape揺らしのDOTween Tween</summary>
+    private Tween _blendShapeTween;
+    /// <summary>SkinnedMeshRenderer（BlendShape用）</summary>
+    private SkinnedMeshRenderer _skinnedMeshRenderer;
```

**2. Start()でSkinnedMeshRenderer検索を追加**

```diff
 _initialLocalEulerAngles = transform.localEulerAngles;
+_skinnedMeshRenderer = GetComponentInChildren<SkinnedMeshRenderer>();
```

**3. OnActionFreakout()の分岐**

```diff
 public void OnActionFreakout()
 {
-    PlayActionAnimation(IsEnabledPoltergeist, _transform, forceVariation, torqueMagnitude, _initialRotation, tiltThreshold,
-        rigidbody, _poltergeistViewModel, _onAction);
+    if (_isWallHanging)
+        PlayWallHangingShakeAnimation(IsEnabledPoltergeist, _transform, _poltergeistViewModel, _onAction);
+    else
+        PlayActionAnimation(IsEnabledPoltergeist, _transform, forceVariation, torqueMagnitude, _initialRotation, tiltThreshold,
+            rigidbody, _poltergeistViewModel, _onAction);
 }
```

**4. 新メソッド追加**

```csharp
/// <summary>
/// 壁掛けオブジェクト用のDOTween揺らし演出
/// </summary>
private void PlayWallHangingShakeAnimation(bool isEnabledPoltergeist, Transform transform,
    PoltergeistViewModel poltergeistViewModel, ReactiveCommand<bool> onAction)
{
    if (!isEnabledPoltergeist || transform == null)
        return;

    _wallHangingShakeSequence?.Kill();
    _wallHangingShakeSequence = DOTween.Sequence()
        .Append(transform.DOShakeRotation(
            duration: 0.6f,
            strength: new Vector3(3f, 0f, 8f),
            vibrato: 12,
            randomness: 90,
            fadeOut: true
        ))
        .OnComplete(() => transform.localRotation = _initialLocalRotation);

    // BlendShape揺らし（SkinnedMeshRendererがある場合のみ）
    if (_skinnedMeshRenderer != null && _skinnedMeshRenderer.sharedMesh.blendShapeCount > 0)
    {
        _blendShapeTween?.Kill();
        float currentWeight = _skinnedMeshRenderer.GetBlendShapeWeight(0);
        _blendShapeTween = DOTween.Sequence()
            .Append(DOTween.To(
                () => _skinnedMeshRenderer.GetBlendShapeWeight(0),
                x => _skinnedMeshRenderer.SetBlendShapeWeight(0, x),
                Mathf.Clamp(currentWeight + 40f, 0f, 100f), 0.3f
            ).SetEase(Ease.OutQuad))
            .Append(DOTween.To(
                () => _skinnedMeshRenderer.GetBlendShapeWeight(0),
                x => _skinnedMeshRenderer.SetBlendShapeWeight(0, x),
                currentWeight, 0.3f
            ).SetEase(Ease.InOutSine));
    }

    onAction.Execute(true);
}
```

**5. OnDestroy()にDOTween停止追加**

```diff
 private void OnDestroy()
 {
+    _wallHangingShakeSequence?.Kill();
+    _blendShapeTween?.Kill();
     _disposableBag.Dispose();
     ...
 }
```

